- `ToolVisualsConfig = { readonly [toolId: string]: ToolVisualEntry | undefined }` — the index signature with `| undefined` is the TypeScript pattern for "lookup by arbitrary key at runtime, where the key may not exist"; this enables safe `config[toolId]?.glbPath ?? null` without type assertions
